pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `aluno` ( `Id_Aluno` smallint(6) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `RA` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL, `Nome` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `Data_Nascimento` date DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_Aluno`), KEY `fk_Id_TurmaAlunoA` (`Id_Turma`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_TurmaAlunoA` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=498 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `avaliacao` ( `Id_Avaliacao` smallint(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Bimestre` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Turma` int(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Serie` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Titulo` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `Bimestre` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `Descricao` varchar(60) DEFAULT NULL, `Data_Avaliacao` date DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_Avaliacao`), KEY `fk_Id_ProfessorAvaliacao` (`Id_Professor`), KEY `fk_ID_BimestreAvaliacao` (`Id_Bimestre`), KEY `Id_Turma` (`Id_Turma`), CONSTRAINT `fk_ID_BimestreAvaliacao` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Bimestre`) REFERENCES `bimestre` (`Id_Bimestre`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorAvaliacao` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=98 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `chamada` ( `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Aluno` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Numero_Chamada` smallint(3) DEFAULT NULL, `Nome` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, KEY `fk_Id_Turma_TurmaAluno` (`Id_Turma`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_Turma_TurmaAluno` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `conteudo_programatico` ( `Id_conteudoProgramatico` smallint(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Bimestre` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Conteudo_Programatico` varchar(600) DEFAULT NULL, `Data_Conteudo` date DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_conteudoProgramatico`), KEY `fk_Id_TurmaconteudoProgramatico` (`Id_Turma`), KEY `fk_Id_BimestreconteudoProgramatico` (`Id_Bimestre`), KEY `fk_Id_ProfessorConteudo_Programatico` (`Id_Professor`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_BimestreconteudoProgramatico` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Bimestre`) REFERENCES `bimestre` (`Id_Bimestre`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorConteudo_Programatico` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorconteudoProgramatico` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_TurmaconteudoProgramatico` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma_professor` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=11 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `frequencia` ( `Id_Aluno` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Bimestre` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Falta` char(1) DEFAULT NULL, `Data` date DEFAULT NULL, KEY `fk_Id_Turma` (`Id_Turma`), KEY `fk_Id_ProfessorFrequencia` (`Id_Professor`), KEY `fk_Id_BimestreFrequencia` (`Id_Bimestre`), KEY `fk_Id_AlunoFrequencia` (`Id_Aluno`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_AlunoFrequencia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Aluno`) REFERENCES `aluno` (`Id_Aluno`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_BimestreFrequencia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Bimestre`) REFERENCES `bimestre` (`Id_Bimestre`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorFrequencia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_Turma` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `media_final` ( `Id_Media` smallint(6) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Id_Aluno` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Bimestre` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Falta_Total` smallint(4) DEFAULT NULL, `Media` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_Media`), KEY `fk_Id_AlunoMedia` (`Id_Aluno`), KEY `fk_Id_TurmaMedia` (`Id_Turma`), KEY `fk_Id_ProfessorMedia` (`Id_Professor`), KEY `fk_Id_BimestreMedia` (`Id_Bimestre`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_AlunoMedia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Aluno`) REFERENCES `aluno` (`Id_Aluno`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_BimestreMedia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Bimestre`) REFERENCES `bimestre` (`Id_Bimestre`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorMedia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_TurmaMedia` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=47 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `nota` ( `Id_Aluno` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Avaliacao` smallint(10) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Bimestre` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Nota` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL, KEY `fk_Id_AlunoNota` (`Id_Aluno`), KEY `fk_Id_TurmaNota` (`Id_Turma`), KEY `fk_Id_ProfessorNota` (`Id_Professor`), KEY `fk_Id_BimestreNota` (`Id_Bimestre`), KEY `fk_AvaliacaoNota` (`Id_Avaliacao`), CONSTRAINT `fk_AvaliacaoNota` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Avaliacao`) REFERENCES `avaliacao` (`Id_Avaliacao`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_AlunoNota` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Aluno`) REFERENCES `aluno` (`Id_Aluno`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_BimestreNota` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Bimestre`) REFERENCES `bimestre` (`Id_Bimestre`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorNota` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_TurmaNota` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma_professor` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `professor` ( `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Usuario` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, KEY `fk_Id_Usuario` (`Id_Usuario`), KEY `fk_Id_Professor` (`Id_Professor`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_Professor` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor_cadastro` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_Usuario` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Usuario`) REFERENCES `usuario` (`Id_Usuario`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `professor_cadastro` ( `Id_Professor` smallint(6) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Nome` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `Disciplina` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `CPF` varchar(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_Professor`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=167 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `turma` ( `Id_Turma` smallint(6) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Serie` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL, `Ano` varchar(5) DEFAULT NULL, `Periodo` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_Turma`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=56 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `turma_professor` ( `Id_Professor` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Id_Turma` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Serie` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL, KEY `fk_Id_ProfessorTurmaProfessor` (`Id_Professor`), KEY `fk_Id_TurmaProfessor` (`Id_Turma`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_ProfessorTurmaProfessor` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Professor`) REFERENCES `professor_cadastro` (`Id_Professor`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE, CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_TurmaProfessor` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Turma`) REFERENCES `turma` (`Id_Turma`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `usuario_aluno` ( `Id_Usuario_Aluno` smallint(6) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Id_Aluno` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL, `Login` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Senha` varchar(12) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`Id_Usuario_Aluno`), KEY `fk_Id_Id_AlunoUsuarioAluno` (`Id_Aluno`), CONSTRAINT `fk_Id_Id_AlunoUsuarioAluno` FOREIGN KEY (`Id_Aluno`) REFERENCES `aluno` (`Id_Aluno`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
